                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Tokyo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1904-02-11">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 11, 1904</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Griscom reports that the declaration of war was issued on the 10th
                    instant.)</p>
